          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a separate baking tray (or two!) with <strong>baking paper</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>meat-free burger patty[ies]</strong> to the lined tray[s] and put in the oven for 10-12 min or until cooked through</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1619786388838-x200.jpg",
