            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your<strong> brioche bun[s] </strong>in half</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1619786398327-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1619786398327-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1619786398327-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1619786398327-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1619786398327-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the patty is cooked through, remove the tray[s] from the oven and top your <strong>patty[ies]</strong> with a <strong>cheese flavour slice</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>brioche halves</strong> to the other side of the tray[s]</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 3-4 min or until the cheeze has melted and the brioche is warmed through</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1619786417440-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1619786417440-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1619786417440-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1619786417440-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1619786417440-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your burger, spread the <strong>Henderson’s mayo </strong>onto the <strong>warmed brioche halves</strong>, then fill with the <strong>Henderson’s caramelised onion</strong>, a <strong>cheezy patty </strong>and some <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> – this is your <strong>Henderson’s Relish meat-free burger</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>black pepper chips</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    }
